# Compass-Centre overview

This workspace centers on the **compass-web** app: Next.js (App Router), React 19, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS v4, ESLint via `eslint-config-next`.

## Where to start

- Package scripts and dependencies: [compass-web/package.json](mdc:compass-web/package.json)
- Next.js config: [compass-web/next.config.ts](mdc:compass-web/next.config.ts)
- App Router root layout (fonts, metadata, global CSS import): [compass-web/src/app/layout.tsx](mdc:compass-web/src/app/layout.tsx)
- Home route UI: [compass-web/src/app/page.tsx](mdc:compass-web/src/app/page.tsx)
- Global styles: [compass-web/src/app/globals.css](mdc:compass-web/src/app/globals.css)

Add new routes under `compass-web/src/app/` as `page.tsx` (and optional `layout.tsx`) per segment folders.
